OL,3,CGreat-grandmother dies after collision
OL,4,Cwith transit van
OL,6,FThe family of a great-grandmother who
OL,7,Fdied after being involved in a
OL,8,Fcollision with a transit van in
OL,9,FMelksham has said that her life has
OL,10,Fbeen cut short.
OL,12,FCheryl Decarteret, 79, was crossing a
OL,13,Froad with her best friend Margaret on
OL,14,FSaturday 27 September when they were
OL,15,Finvolved in a collision with a
OL,16,Freversing transit van.
OL,18,FFive days later, Cheryl's daughters
OL,19,Fand son made the decision to turn off
OL,20,Fher life support.
