OL,6,F"Standing there and watching her,
OL,7,Fwatching them take out the tubes,
OL,8,Fknowing you've got minutes left and
OL,9,Fthat's it, that's been the really
OL,10,Fdevastating part," said Hayley
OL,11,FCharman, Cheryl's daughter.
OL,13,F"That's the part that's hit the
OL,14,Fgrandchildren, that's the part that's
OL,15,Fhit me.
