OL,6,F"Up until now, there's things that
OL,7,Fhave needed to be done. We've had to
OL,8,Fget on, we've had to make decisions.
OL,9,FThere's still been that tiny glimmer
OL,10,Fof hope, but turning up today, you
OL,11,Fknew it was just gone. There was no
OL,12,Fhope left."
OL,14,FPolice were called to Lowborne in
OL,15,Fcentral Melksham just after 1.30pm on
OL,16,FSaturday afternoon. The friends were
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital, where Margaret Shaw
OL,18,Fremains with life-threatening injuries.
