OL,4,Cwith transit van
OL,6,FA 25-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and drug driving. He
OL,9,Fhas been released on bail while
OL,10,Fenquiries continue.
OL,12,FCheryl retired three years ago after
OL,13,Fworking since the age of 18.
OL,15,FHayley told ITV West Country: "That's
OL,16,Fwhat kind of makes this so much worse.
OL,17,FThis was supposed to be her time now.
