OL,6,F"She took her retirement and she was
OL,7,Fsupposed to be able to enjoy that and
OL,8,Fdo what she loved doing. And Margaret,
OL,9,Fthey did everything together. It's
OL,10,Fjust been cut short, so short."
OL,12,FWiltshire Police have launched an
OL,13,Furgent appeal to the public for CCTV
OL,14,Fand dashcam footage to support their
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,FPC Leigh Mayhew said: "A number of
OL,18,Fwitnesses were spoken to at the scene
OL,19,Fbut it's believed there may be other
OL,20,Fwitnesses who were perhaps driving by
OL,21,Fwho we haven't spoken with yet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
