OL,6,F"It's really important that if you
OL,7,Fwitnessed what happened or have any
OL,8,Ffootage that you come forward."
OL,10,FCheryl's family are appealing to the
OL,11,Fpublic to "be brave and come forward".
OL,13,F"I can understand that going to the
OL,14,Fpolice with something you've seen can
OL,15,Fbe scary, but my mum has lost her
OL,16,Flife. Her best friend is still
OL,17,Ffighting for hers," Hayley said.
